## My process

### Built with

- Semantic HTML5 markup
- CSS
- CSS Preprocessor SASS

### What I learned

This is an extremely fun project I'm working on and I hope to complete it soon.

See a code snippet below:

```sass

.footer {
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 10rem 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: $color-pastel-purple;
    &__logo-box {
        text-align: center;
    }
    &__logo {
        width: 15rem;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }
}

```

